c', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/77007/', '', 'Interferon alfa-n1, Oprelvekin, Elapegademase, Peginterferon alfa-2a, Interferon alfacon-1, Sargramostim, Histamine, Aldesleukin, Pegademase, Pegfilgrastim, Interferon alfa-2b, More', 'Golimumab, Ustekinumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Ravulizumab, Mycophenolic acid, Tacrolimus, Abatacept, Upadacitinib, Anakinra, More', 1767369485);
