c function is advisable.', 'Synergism', 'The use of naltrexone with other potentially hepatotoxic agents should be avoided whenever possible (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/77098/', '', 'Golimumab, Ustekinumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Mycophenolic acid, Tacrolimus, Abatacept, Upadacitinib, More', 'Oliceridine, Oxymorphone, Tapentadol, Butorphanol, Dezocine, Opium, Dextropropoxyphene, Pentazocine, Dihydrocodeine, Naloxone, Codeine, More', 1767369485);
